<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset="UTF-8")
        meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
        title Metric Imperial Converter
    body
        .container

            h1 Metric/Imperial Converter API
            img(src="/img/github_icon_48px.svg", alt="github icon" class="git_repo")

            p An API Endpoint to convert Metric to Imperial units and vice versa.

            h3 
                span kg ⇄ lbs     
                span km ⇄ mi     
                span l ⇄ gal

            h3 API URL
            //- p ~/api/convert
            p= api_url

            h3 Examples Request
            p.
                ~/api/convert?input=4gal <br>
                ~/api/convert?input=3.5L <br>
                ~/api/convert?input=1.5/5mi <br>

            h3 Example Response
            p.
                {
                    “initNum”: 1,
                    “initUnit”: “kg”,
                    “returnNum”: 2.20462,
                    “returnUnit”: “lbs”,
                    “string”: “1 kilograms converts to 2.20462 pounds”
                }

            h3 Implementation
            img(src="/img/implementation_demo.png", alt="implementation")

            h3 Front-End
            include ./form

